{"tid":125990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日日訓教比野咬 係咪木蝨","createTime":"2017-02-19T03:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T13:53:16.000Z","uid":10912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71d2a8567c0246ef95b404c7aaba1497dd60dbad","tid":125990,"uid":10912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母日日訓醒都有幾粒野痕到仆街<br />\n蚊香 艾草 香薰都點過哂所以應該唔係蚊<br />\n試過拎起床褥睇又冇野<br />\n見人話咩debug粉 係邊有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎頂唔住想死"},{"pid":"6efc5431efea429a69032fe3fc3c09be314d771d","tid":125990,"uid":73628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"4c5c1b256b6eb5c1a160fa940b5bb33241d41f64","tid":125990,"uid":11997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母日日訓醒都有幾粒野痕到仆街<br />\n蚊香 艾草 香薰都點過哂所以應該唔係蚊<br />\n試過拎起床褥睇又冇野<br />\n見人話咩debug粉 係邊有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎頂唔住想死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前比木蝨玩左半年 最後用DE粉成功擊退咗 <br />\n真係要勤啲灑同埋灑多啲地方<br />\n<br />\n啲木蝨多數喺床架度，留意下<br />\n<br />\nDE粉上網一search就有，我用嗰間係去旺角樓上鋪交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申非打手"},{"pid":"633a138fd687738e296cc40a640e3cc7953b167a","tid":125990,"uid":11997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母日日訓醒都有幾粒野痕到仆街<br />\n蚊香 艾草 香薰都點過哂所以應該唔係蚊<br />\n試過拎起床褥睇又冇野<br />\n見人話咩debug粉 係邊有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎頂唔住想死</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n要分辨係咪木蝨就要睇下你地床單床褥嗰啲有無啲黑色一點點，如果有就係佢地啲屎嚟 如果無就唔洗擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df730f9e4fe031d2d24a43aaddb8f7c6c795ccda","tid":125990,"uid":66827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"